We depart from the SARAH standar and
will install SARAH directly in the primary
directory.

$ ./configure --disable-whizard --disable-higgsbounds --disable-higgssignals

$ rm link
$ mv real_name link

To update
$ rm -rf link
$ mv real_name link

Check status, add possible new files

$ rm -rf calchep/ madgraph/ micromegas/ SARAH/ SPHENO/ SSP/ tarballs/ 

Return back 
$ rsync -avxz toolbox-1.2.8/ toolbox